       <h1 class="entry-title"> <a href="http://www.zhangzishi.cc/%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e5%b8%ae%e6%9c%8b%e5%8f%8b%e8%bf%bd%e5%80%ba%e7%9a%84%e7%bb%8f%e5%8e%86-%e5%86%8d%e4%b9%9f%e4%b8%8d%e6%95%a2%e6%95%99%e5%88%ab%e4%ba%ba%e8%bf%bd%e5%80%ba%e4%ba%86.html" rel="bookmark">一次帮朋友追债的经历……再也不敢教别人追债了……</a> </h1> 
       <div class="comments-link"> 
        <a href="http://www.zhangzishi.cc/%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e5%b8%ae%e6%9c%8b%e5%8f%8b%e8%bf%bd%e5%80%ba%e7%9a%84%e7%bb%8f%e5%8e%86-%e5%86%8d%e4%b9%9f%e4%b8%8d%e6%95%a2%e6%95%99%e5%88%ab%e4%ba%ba%e8%bf%bd%e5%80%ba%e4%ba%86.html#comments" title="《一次帮朋友追债的经历……再也不敢教别人追债了……》上的评论">2条回复</a> 
