      <header class="entry-header"> 
       <h1 class="entry-title"> <a href="http://www.zhangzishi.cc/20150126gg.html" rel="bookmark">哈哈哈哈，胡彦斌，你活该是只单身狗</a> </h1> 
       <div class="comments-link"> 
        <a href="http://www.zhangzishi.cc/20150126gg.html#respond" title="《哈哈哈哈，胡彦斌，你活该是只单身狗》上的评论"><span class="leave-reply">发表回复</span></a> 
